<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_487_r1l2">Bıſchof cʒu Eẏſtet </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_487_r1l3"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Als vvir <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> nehſt <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_487_r1l4">von Göcʒen viſchers <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> vvegen darauf Jr vns <expan>vvıd<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_487_r1l5"><expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt vvie er <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> noch etwas gult beleib </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_487_r1l6"><expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir Jn beſant vnd cʒerede geſacʒt vnd er <expan>ſp<ex>ri</ex>cht</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_487_r1l7">vvaʒ er <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>belıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſeẏ daʒ hab er mit den <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_487_r1l8">abgerechent vnd Jn das beʒalt / So hab er ein viſchwaſſer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_487_r1l9">von <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gehabt / daʒ habt Jr Jm <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> des etwıeuil </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_487_r1l10">Jar ſein vnd het Jr Jm das gelaſſen / vvas er <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_487_r1l11">dauon getan ſolt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> daʒ het er <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> getan / Nu <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_487_r1l12">daʒ Jr das beſteen laſſen vvöllet bıſʒ ewr gnad <expan>ſelb<ex>er</ex></expan> her </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_487_r1l13">kum / <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> ob </del> Jr ſuſt ẏemand her ſchıcken vvolt / daʒ Jr dem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_487_r1l14"><expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> befulht / So vvolten wir <expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> rede vnd auch den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_487_r1l15"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> gen <expan>einand<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan> / vnd ob wir ſie niht gütlıchen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_487_r1l16"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>einen</expan> möhten / des rechten von dem <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> helffen / als </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_487_r1l17">wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hochw<ex>irdikeit</ex></expan> vor <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd getrawen <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_487_r1l19">vvol daʒ Jr es durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vvıllen tun vnd Jn mit der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_487_r1l20"><expan>geiſtlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>ladu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> vnbeſwert laſſen wöllet / das wollen etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_487_r1l21"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_487" id="243r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Bischof czu Eystet </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re,</expan> als wir <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> nehst
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von Göczen Vischers,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s,</expan> wegen, darauf ir uns
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie er
                            <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> noch etwas gult beleib;
                                <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir in besant und cze rede gesaczt und er
                                <expan>sp<ex>ri</ex>cht</expan>, waz er
                            <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>belib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sey, daz hab er mit den
                            <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> abgerechent und in das bezalt. So hab er
                        ein vischwasser von <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gehabt, daz habt ir im
                                <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan>, des etwievil jar sein, und het ir
                        im das gelassen, was er <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> davon getan solt
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz het er <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        getan. Nu <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir das besteen lassen wöllet,
                        bisz ewr gnad <expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan> her kum
                            <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> ir sust yemand her schicken wolt, daz ir
                        dem <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> befulht, so wolten wir
                                <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> rede und auch den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> gen <expan>einand<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan> und, ob wir sie niht gütlichen
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>einen</expan> möhten, des rechten von dem
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> helffen, als wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hochw<ex>irdikeit</ex></expan> vor
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n;</expan> und getrawen <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wol, daz ir es durch
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen tun und in mit der
                                <expan>geistlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ladu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> unbeswert lassen wöllet. Das wollen etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
